text: Bo' Selecta! is a British sketch comedy television programme. It includes skits parodying celebrities, including Michael Jackson, Craig David, and Mel B. The show had mixed reviews. It began on 6 September 2002 and ended on 18 December 2009. == Other websites == * Category:2002 British television series debuts Category:2009 British television series endings Category:2000s British comedy television series Category:2000s LGBT television series Category:2000s satirical television series Category:British LGBT television programmes Category:British satirical television series Category:Channel 4 comedy Category:LGBT comedy television series Category:Television sketch shows Category:English-language television programs
